  "description": "<p><u>Requirements</u></p><ol><li>Possess an <strong>approved opticianry qualification</strong>. <strong>Provisional Opticians are welcome! </strong>Please refer to: https://www.healthprofessionals.gov.sg/oob/registration-as-an-optometrist-and-optician/list-of-approved-optometry-and-opticianry-qualifications for more information. </li><li>Registered under Singapore <strong>OOB</strong> (Optometrists & Opticians Board)</li></ol><p><u>Location</u><br />Tampines Central, Toa Payoh, Upper Serangoon<br /><br /><u>Responsibilities</u></p><ul><li>Make sales recommendations on products</li><li>Conduct refraction for customers</li><li>Interpret prescriptions written by other eyecare practitioners</li><li>Dispensing & spectacles adjustment</li><li>Customer Relations management</li><li>Daily shop operations</li></ul>",
